    h2 Packaging your mod
    ul
      li Play without using eclipse
      li Allow friends/family to play your mod
      li Allow servers to run your mod so lots of people can play with it
      li Put your mod in an easy to download format online

  section
    h2 Packaging your mod
    ul
      li Edit build.gradle and change the group and archiveBaseName entries
      li Open a command prompt and run <code>gradlew build</code>
      li 
        |In the folder build – lib, you will find your Jar file: you can post
        |this on a website for other people to use.

